				"speakerSlotDescription": [
					{}
				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Crimson the dinosaur is one of the animals who will participate in the doppelganger-dribbles attack. Player can examine him and realise Crimson isn't angry, he's starving. If the player feeds him some meat, he is so busy eating during the attack that he doesn't participate.\r\nIn the bottom branch, he's so hungry that he's on the brink of losing his mind - he's snapping, furious, and all he craves is meat."
				}
